description: Bygg Partner i Dalarna Holding AB engages in the construction work, building services, and property development. The company is headquartered in Borlange, Dalarna and currently employs 522 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-12-05. The firm operates as a provider of construction works, building services and property development, among others. The firm offers a wide range of services within residential, commercial, industrial, office and public buildings areas. The firm operates domestically, on the territory of Dalarna, Malardalen, Stockholm, Uppsala. The firm's offerings include Project development, refurbishment, extension, renovation, pipe replacement, among others. The firm operates through one subsidiary, namely Juf Byggnadsstallningar AB, which is involved in the secure scaffolding, fall protection and weather protection.
name: ByggPartner i Dalarna Holding AB (publ)
